Hello,
We have started making our Marker Converter available as a standalone application on macOS and iOS. It is intended for enterprise customers and projects or systems that do not allow network access. The initial version contains most of the basic features, with more to be added soon. If there's something you're missing, let us know.
Purchase on AppStore.

The app supports light & dark theme.

Would you be interested in standalone, offline versions of our Subtitle Tool, ALE Converter or EDL Converter?
Please let us know if you are interested, and tell us which features you would like us to prioritize. Send us an email: support@editingtools.io

Your EditingTools.io Team


